"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_enigma_demonic_conversion_lua_Description"	"Sacrifice health to summon a wraith that possesses the Void Arrow ability. If the wraith is already summoned, restore its health to full and extend its duration.<br><br>For every %upgrade_kill_count% non-hero enemies killed by the wraith, Enigma gains 1 stack of Demonic Mastery. If the wraith kills an enemy hero, Enigma instantly gains %hero_kill_upgrade% stacks of Demonic Mastery.<br><br>Each stack of Demonic Mastery increases the wraith’s level by 1, granting %mana_regen% increased mana regeneration and %health_gain% bonus health, while enhancing the wraith’s abilities.<br><br>When Enigma or the wraith dies, Enigma loses %death_lose% stacks of Demonic Mastery."
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_enigma_demonic_conversion_lua_Lore"	"Enigma possesses the ability to draw its form into another dimension—giving rise to three dark void wraiths that hunt the corporeal plane."
